lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Sept. 23 -- Senator Norris, Independent, asserted today that repeal of the Neutrality Act would mean war and he voiced his doubts that Congress would approve a declaration, of war at the present time.
abstract: Says Neutrality Act repeal means war
